title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Salvage Yard Robberies
content: Visit your Salvage Yard to assess schemes for stealing the Bravado Buffalo EVX (Muscle), Lampadati Viseris (Sports Classic), and Pegassi Toros (SUV). Once you’ve chosen your target, the planning wall inside your Salvage Yard outlines all the steps for these multi-part operations and the vehicle’s whereabouts.
